8	115	Copy of RAZ Clone	SLLPJ-1-1	50.00	https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-li5zabuvgu/products/115/images/395/raz-ltx-thumb__97978.1744299356.1280.1280__46096.1744656651.386.513.jpg?c=1	Raz DC25000 25k Puffs 50mg 16mL Disposables *Display of 5*\nIntroducing the NEW Raz Vape DC25000, a revolutionary disposable vape device that pushes the boundaries of longevity and satisfaction. Crafted by RAZ, this innovative vape offers an astounding 25,000 puffs, setting a new standard in the world of disposable vaping. \nKey Features:25,000 Puffs: Unprecedented longevity for extended vaping enjoyment.Advanced Coil and Battery Systems: Ensures consistent, flavorful sessions with superior performance.16mL Pre-Filled E-Liquid: Experience a variety of RAZ vape flavors with smooth nicotine delivery.800mAh Type-C Rechargeable Battery: Long-lasting power for extended vaping sessions.Two Vaping Modes: Choose between Regular Mode (25,000 puffs) and Boost Mode (15,000 puffs) for personalized vaping experience.Mega HD Display Screen: Clear and vibrant display for easy monitoring of battery and e-liquid levels.Vaping Animation &amp; Charging Animation: A visually engaging experience for modern vapers.Wattage Adjustment: Customize your vaping experience with adjustable wattage settings.Light &amp; Dark Modes: Choose your preferred display mode for personalized style.Safety Features: Includes short-circuit protection and overcharging protection for peace of mind.Long-Lasting Satisfaction: Enjoy extended vaping sessions without the need for frequent replacements.Variety of Flavors: Explore a range of RAZ vape flavors for a diverse vaping experience.User-Friendly Design: Sleek and practical design for easy use and portability.Customizable Experience: Choose between different vaping modes and wattage settings for a tailored vaping experience.Safety and Protection: Built-in safety features ensure a secure and worry-free vaping experience.\nFlavors:\n\n Banguin Sour Berries: Indulge in the tangy burst of sour berries with every vape of Banguin Sour Berries. A delightful blend of tartness and sweetness that will leave your taste buds craving for more.\n Blue Razz Ice: Chill out with the refreshing flavor of Blue Razz Ice. A combination of blue raspberry sweetness with a hint of icy coolness, perfect for hot summer days.\n Blueberry Watermelon: Experience the juicy fusion of ripe blueberries and succulent watermelon in every puff. Blueberry Watermelon is a delightful fruity blend that will invigorate your senses.\n Cherry Strapple: Enjoy the harmonious marriage of cherry and apple with a twist of strawberry in Cherry Strapple. A delightful concoction that is both sweet and tart, sure to satisfy your cravings.\n Georgia Peach: Take a trip to the peach orchards of Georgia with Georgia Peach vape juice. Sweet, juicy, and bursting with flavor, this e-liquid captures the essence of ripe peaches in every inhale.\n Iced Blue Dragon: Embark on an icy adventure with Iced Blue Dragon. This exotic blend of blueberries and dragon fruit is enhanced with a cool menthol breeze, providing a refreshing vaping experience.\n Miami Mint: Cool off with the refreshing taste of Miami Mint. This minty e-liquid offers a burst of icy freshness with every puff, perfect for those who crave a clean and invigorating flavor.\n Night Crawler: Dive into the depths of flavor with Night Crawler. This mysterious blend of fruits and berries is shrouded in darkness, offering a unique and intense vaping experience.\n Raspberry Lemonade: Quench your thirst with the zesty goodness of Raspberry Lemonade. Tangy raspberries are combined with tart lemonade to create a refreshing vape juice that is perfect for summer.\n Sour Apple Watermelon: Experience a sour twist on classic fruit flavors with Sour Apple Watermelon. Crisp green apples are paired with juicy watermelon, creating a mouth-puckering sensation that will leave you wanting more.\n Sour Watermelon Peach: Get ready for a flavor explosion with Sour Watermelon Peach. This sour and sweet blend of watermelon and peach is sure to tantalize your taste buds and keep you coming back for more.\n\nIdeal for vape enthusiasts looking for a high-quality, long-lasting, and innovative vaping solution, the Raz DC25000 offers unmatched performance and satisfaction. Elevate your vaping experience with the Raz DC25000 - order now and embark on a new adventure in vaping!	470	t	[{"id": 161, "sku": "RZDC25K-BSB-1", "price": "50", "stock_level": 10, "option_values": [{"id": 159, "label": "Bangin Sour Berries", "option_id": 116, "option_display_name": "Flavor"}]}, {"id": 162, "sku": "RZDC25K-BRI-1", "price": "50", "stock_level": 10, "option_values": [{"id": 160, "label": "Blue Raz Ice", "option_id": 116, "option_display_name": "Flavor"}]}, {"id": 163, "sku": "RZDC25K-BW-1", "price": "50", "stock_level": 10, "option_values": [{"id": 161, "label": "Blueberry Watermelon", "option_id": 116, "option_display_name": "Flavor"}]}, {"id": 164, "sku": "RZDC25K-CS-1", "price": "50", "stock_level": 10, "option_values": [{"id": 162, "label": "Cherry Strapple", "option_id": 116, "option_display_name": "Flavor"}]}, {"id": 165, "sku": "RZDC25K-GP-1", "price": "50", "stock_level": 10, "option_values": [{"id": 163, "label": "Georgia Peach", "option_id": 116, "option_display_name": "Flavor"}]}, {"id": 166, "sku": "SLLPJ-1-IC-1", "price": "50", "stock_level": 10, "option_values": [{"id": 164, "label": "Iced Blue Dragon", "option_id": 116, "option_display_name": "Flavor"}]}, {"id": 167, "sku": "SLLPJ-1-MI-1", "price": "50", "stock_level": 10, "option_values": [{"id": 165, "label": "Miami Mint", "option_id": 116, "option_display_name": "Flavor"}]}, {"id": 168, "sku": "SLLPJ-1-NI-1", "price": "50", "stock_level": 10, "option_values": [{"id": 166, "label": "Night Crawler", "option_id": 116, "option_display_name": "Flavor"}]}, {"id": 169, "sku": "SLLPJ-1-RA-111", "price": "50", "stock_level": 10, "option_values": [{"id": 167, "label": "Raspberry Limeade", "opt